  <name>Operational Dashboard</name>
  <summary>Operational calendar KPIs, targets, and trends in Nextcloud</summary>
  <description><![CDATA[Opsdash is an operations dashboard for teams that run their planning in Nextcloud Calendar.

It converts raw events into clear weekly and monthly insights so you can track workload, pace against targets, and spot drift early.

## What you get
- KPI dashboard for totals, active days, busiest slots, and category mix
- Target tracking for calendars and categories with pacing and forecast context
- Balance and trend widgets to compare periods and detect over/under-allocation
- Notes, presets, and profile import/export for repeatable reporting workflows
- Guided onboarding that gets a new setup ready in minutes

## Built for Nextcloud
- Runs fully inside Nextcloud (no external analytics service)
- Per-user preferences are stored server-side
- CSRF-protected write endpoints and standard Nextcloud permission model

If you need a practical planning cockpit on top of existing calendar data, Opsdash gives you fast visibility without leaving your Nextcloud instance.]]></description>
